title: Linus Torvalds Announces First Linux Kernel 6.6 Release Candidate
description:
Linus Torvalds announced the general availability of the first Release Candidate version of the upcoming Linux 6.6 kernel series for public testing.

title: KDE Frameworks 5.110 Adds Support for the QOI Image Format to All KDE Apps
description:
